# neckarshore-website env-vars
# Copy to .env.local for local development. .env.local is gitignored.
# Production + Preview values are set in Vercel dashboard separately.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Analytics read-only access (GET /api/track)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Generate via: openssl rand -hex 32
# Required for: GET /api/track (analytics read endpoint).
# POST /api/track (visitor-ping via navigator.sendBeacon) stays public — no
# token needed. Browsers never send this token; only server-side callers do.
#
# Fail-closed: if this is missing or empty in the deployed env, GET returns
# 401 even with a token provided in the request.
#
# dr-sommer Z1 Finding 1.1 — see omnopsis-planning/docs/plans/api-track-auth-hardening.md
ANALYTICS_READ_TOKEN=
